metadata.name: Halloweiners #1
metadata.description:
Halloweiners: the genesis art collection by Pup&Dump. 

With one Halloweiner, you get one free mint to all fine art Pup&Dump future collections. 

No Discord. Twitter, Smart Contract, and Website Only. All Future Collections will be generated from the official Pup&Dump Wallet 0xBd6c591A471f897a0a04e22E90450a5Ae9dFA40e

Royalties for this, and all future collections, will forever be 2.5% to set a precedent that high royalties, in addition to marketplace fees, are not acceptable.
